data.description: Discover your dream home at 14281 Hunter Creek! Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this property offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Offering 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Step inside to discover spacious living areas, modern amenities, and a surprise bonus room not accounted for in the square footage. Imagine the potential - convert the bonus room back into a garage, creating a 3-car tandem space. Plus, relish the convenience of room for a small RV and did I mention the convenience of covered parking! Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
